data.description: Beautiful clean two story four bedroom three and a half bath home. Main bedroom down stairs with large bath and walk in closet, two living spaces, dining and breakfast room and an open floor kitchen, walk in pantry. Three bedrooms up stairs. One of the bedrooms has its own full bathroom with a walk in closet. large game room/loft. High ceiling entrance and long hallway with a lot of space to enjoy. NEW ROOF, water softener and the backyard is flat with a clean metal shed. Two car garage with remote door opener and key pad accessible on all doors.
